    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've talked to people. they just say \"time heals\" or try to cheer me up, but they don't get it. it doesn't feel like it's going to heal. it just feels like i'm drowning in this house. i just want it to stop. i want the noise and the sadness and the heavy feeling to just... end. is it really so wrong to just want peace?",
